:{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 116.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' Friend, let's not beat around the bush here &mdash; the thing is, {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|I want to reach out personally to team up with the Astral Express.}}
:{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 117.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' I told you, I'm just not interested in scrambling for "the Legacy." I just came to Penacony for work. I'm here to retrieve some lost property for the IPC, if you catch my drift... I'm talking ownership of this "frontier prison."
:{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 118.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' This has all become a bad debt thanks to the {{Rubi|Cancer of All Worlds|Stellaron}}. The IPC has tried sitting down for negotiations time and again, but The Family wouldn't even take our calls.
:{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 119.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' You have no idea how difficult these people are to deal with. Put it this way &mdash; they've hushed up the existence of "Death" before, so they can definitely cover up any news about Robin's death.
:{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 120.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' It'll just quietly float off like a bubble and pop, nobody ever being the wiser...
:{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 121.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' That's not fair, right? So then, friend, I need your help.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} What kind of help?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I've got something on right now.
::{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 122.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' That's fine. I'm not forcing you.
::{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 123.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' But I'm really not asking for much, so why don't you at least hear me out, okay?
