:{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 126.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' I have but only one goal: The Family's front door is like a high wall, and to tear the whole thing down I'll have to dig out a few chunks first. Once I find a weak point, the IPC will have plenty of means.
:{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 127.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' Now we have our chance. So long as we can {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|get to the truth behind her death}}, we can have justice for Robin while also gaining a valuable bargaining chip for bringing The Family to the table.
:{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 128.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' Truly a once-in-a-blue-moon opportunity... I've been investigating and making lots of friends all over Penacony precisely for this very moment.
:{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 129.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' This tragic news would be extremely bad for The Family, so they'll be doing everything they can to stop it leaking &mdash; especially to the IPC.
:{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 130.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' But I trust there are still a few factions that remain exceptions, and that's why I need you all. The reputation of the Astral Express precedes you, and the Harmony will give you the fairest of appraisals.
:{{A|VO chapter3 8 aventurine 131.ogg}} '''Aventurine:''' You get to find out really what happened and seek justice, and I get to put it toward completing my mission for the IPC... It's what you call a win-win situation.
